@startuml seq-rf01-registrar-lancamento
title RF01 + RF03 - Registrar lancamento e publicar evento

actor Comerciante
participant "Front Blazor" as Front
participant "API Gateway" as APIGW
participant "API Lancamentos" as ApiLanc
database "Aurora / PostgreSQL" as DB
queue "SQS lancamento-criado" as SQS

Comerciante -> Front: Preenche credito/debito
Front -> APIGW: POST /api/lancamentos\nBearer JWT
APIGW -> APIGW: Valida JWT e scope\nlancamentos:write
APIGW -> ApiLanc: Encaminha request

ApiLanc -> ApiLanc: Valida regras RN01.x\n(valor, descricao, data, tipo)
alt Dados invalidos
    ApiLanc --> APIGW: 400 Bad Request
    APIGW --> Front: Erro de validacao
else Dados validos
    ApiLanc -> DB: INSERT lancamento
    DB --> ApiLanc: Commit OK
    ApiLanc -> SQS: Publica LancamentoCriadoEvent
    note right of SQS: RN03.1 - evento apos persistencia
    ApiLanc --> APIGW: 201 Created
    APIGW --> Front: Sucesso
    Front --> Comerciante: Confirmacao imediata
    note over Comerciante, SQS: Consolidacao ocorre de forma assincrona (RF04)
end

@enduml
